                <p>Average age of ours readers is ${AverageReaderAge} years.</p>
                <p>Average time of using Librarium is ${AverageTimeOfUsingLibrary} days.</p>
                <p>Total quantity of orders is ${QuantityOfOrdersInAllPeriod}.</p>
